=======================================================================
                               OVERVIEW
=======================================================================

-----------------------------------------------------------------------
INTRODUCTION
-----------------------------------------------------------------------
The MCR Viewer is a Perl script that enables the user to execute and use the mcr_viewer tool.
This tool provides a mechanism to view modem call records....

-----------------------------------------------------------------------
SYSTEM REQUIREMENTS
-----------------------------------------------------------------------
The MCR Viewer Perl script has been tested successfully on SunOS ver 5.6 and Perl ver  5.005_03 built for sun4-solaris.
 To use MCR Viewer, the following requirements must be met:
*
*
*
