=======================================================================
                        INSTALLATION AND CONFIGURATION
=======================================================================

-----------------------------------------------------------------------
PACKAGE CONTENT
-----------------------------------------------------------------------
MCR Viewer is supplied, as a Perl (.pl) script as part of a tar gzip archive, and consists of the following files:

File                            Description
----                            -----------
devlist.dat                                  - device list
lwt-start.lbi                       - html (start) template
lwt-end.lbi                                  - html (end) template
mcr_viewer.pl                       - Perl script
mcrv_bn.gif                                  - graphic
Readme.txt                      - this file
supportal_spot.gif              - graphic



-----------------------------------------------------------------------
INSTALLATION NOTES
-----------------------------------------------------------------------
Follow this procedure to install MCR Viewer:

1. Un tar/gzip the archive to the default directory:
        /opt/CSCOlwt

2.  Edit $LWTCONF to point to the config folder
        (for example:$LWTCONF = "/opt/CSCOlwt/conf")

3. Create the file /opt/CSCOlwt/conf/lwt.cfg

4. Create the file /opt/CSCOlwt/conf/devlist.dat


