                        ABOUT COE-IAE
=======================================================================
 The Center of Excellence for Internet Access Engineering (COE-IAE)  is a growing team of professionals dedicated to the s
upport of Internet Access Engineering (IAE) through the development of knowledge based tools and procedures that enable ra
pid delivery of high quality, integrated solutions to the user community.

The COE-IAE strives to:
                *  Create partnerships between Cisco, academia, industry, and the local technical
                 community to enable rapid IAE tools and techniques development.

         * Foster the rapid transfer of generated knowledge to all who can use it.

         *  Develop "real world, best practice" IAE tools and techniques that successfully
          scale to both Internet Service Providers (ISP) and enterprise computing
           environments and enable greater product absorption.

          *  Develop standards and practices for future IAE certification programs.

